description: Introducing unit 4K at Pier 4, Boston’s premier waterfront property in the heart of the Seaport! This sun-splashed 1 bed + Den with 1.5 bathrooms offers a beautiful open floor-plan with private balcony and magnificent unobstructed views of Boston Harbor. This meticulously designed residence features high-end custom built-ins with abundant storage throughout, custom banquette dining area, 10 foot ceilings, walnut flooring, and gourmet chef's kitchen boasting sleek cabinetry, white marble island, and Gaggenau appliances. The master suite overlooks the harbor and features a gorgeous marble bathroom with double vanity and walk-in shower. Additional den is perfect for home office, nursery, or out of town guests. Pier 4 is a boutique style building consisting of 106 homes, offering a suite of amenities including a state of the art gym, golf simulator, 24 hour concierge, doorman, resident lounge, fire pit, grill and common terrace overlooking the water. Includes one deeded parking space.
